202
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:02,820
Bolo to Shenzongove rozhodnutie.

203
00:15:02,820 --> 00:15:07,060
Spáchal velezradu, zločin čo sa neodpúšťa.

204
00:15:07,060 --> 00:15:10,270
