212
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:36,080
Tang Bonian z minulosti vás sledoval, lebo nič nemal.

213
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,720
Má jedine svoj život.

214
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:41,360
