224
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:37,070
Aké bláznovstvo!

225
00:16:37,730 --> 00:16:42,660
<i> Tang Zhirong, to dievča úmyselne provokovalo Yuwen Zi.</i>

226
00:16:42,660 --> 00:16:45,640
